title: Man Down (TV series)
description: Dan (Greg Davies) is a childish idiot trapped in an adult's life, helped along by his uniquely dysfunctional best friends, Jo (Roisin Conaty) and Brian (Mike Wozniak). His inability to navigate the simplest of life's tasks, whilst a listless teaching career and daily humiliation and torment by his Father in Series 1 (played by the late Rik Mayall) and, in Series 2, his aunt Nesta (Stephanie Cole), conspire to keep this Man Down
